            <thetext>As with solution of bug #5873, we discovered this bug. Toolbar Button inherits from Atom. In Atom you want to have icon left, and the label takes all the space with is needed.
This behaviour is not wanted for Toolbar Button. You want to have icon and label centered as one block. Label should use at least space as needed.

Also see:
http://hacks.mozilla.org/2010/04/the-css-3-flexible-box-model/</thetext>
          </long_desc>
